description:
MicrosoftKeyImporter is a KeePass 2.x plugin for importing XML key files from MSDN and TechNet.

#### How to use
* Open KeePass and choose __File -> Import__
* Under the __General__ section, select __MSDN__ or __TechNet Keys XML__.
* Select the KeysExport.xml file that you've exported from MSDN or TechNet and click __OK__.
* [FAQ](https://github.com/svickn/MicrosoftKeyImporterPlugin#faq)
summary: KeePass 2 import plugin for XML key files from MSDN and TechNet
author: Stacy Vicknair
